00:44:03,039 --> 00:44:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se mora šali da je niku.

1112
00:44:04,460 --> 00:44:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, još ima...

1113
00:44:05,659 --> 00:44:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, idući tjedan

1114
00:44:06,539 --> 00:44:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] će biti zadnji,

1115
00:44:07,460 --> 00:44:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] bit će udrni,

1116
00:44:08,039 --> 00:44:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] sigurno će biti tu nečega.

1117
00:44:09,420 --> 00:44:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih primijetio jedan paradoksa,

1118
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je da...

1119
00:44:11,460 --> 00:44:13,639
[SPEAKER_01] Sa svih strana su mene...

1120
00:44:13,639 --> 00:44:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] Meni govorili da sam se...

1121
00:44:15,079 --> 00:44:16,719
[SPEAKER_01] Da sam ja udjelo s Mandićem,

1122
00:44:16,719 --> 00:44:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] što je notarna neistina

1123
00:44:18,260 --> 00:44:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje su...

1124
00:44:19,340 --> 00:44:21,300
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje su govorili da ga ja ne pljujem.

1125
00:44:21,300 --> 00:44:23,519
[SPEAKER_01] A u isto to vrijeme svi ti koji su govorili

1126
00:44:23,519 --> 00:44:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] da ja ne pljujem Mandića,

1127
00:44:24,659 --> 00:44:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] isto njega nisu pljujovali,

1128
00:44:25,840 --> 00:44:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] nego onda bila ta ono...

1129
00:44:27,280 --> 00:44:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] Gromoglasna tišina.

1130
00:44:28,260 --> 00:44:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] To je s jedna strana.

1131
00:44:29,500 --> 00:44:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] S druge strane pojavio se

1132
00:44:30,900 --> 00:44:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] niz lažnih profila,

1133
00:44:33,260 --> 00:44:33,940
[SPEAKER_01] to moram reći.

1134
00:44:33,940 --> 00:44:35,280
[SPEAKER_01] Znači to prije nije bilo...

1135
00:44:35,280 --> 00:44:37,619
[SPEAKER_02] Priča sam čak i sa Draženkom.

1136
00:44:37,619 --> 00:44:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, ja bih tu napravio distinkciju,

1137
00:44:40,199 --> 00:44:40,679
[SPEAKER_01] jednu bitnu.

1138
00:44:40,679 --> 00:44:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji, ajmo reći,

1139
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:44,820
[SPEAKER_01] lažni profil ovih običnih ljudi,

1140
00:44:44,820 --> 00:44:46,340
[SPEAKER_01] koje čak i treba se jedna strana razumijeti.

1141
00:44:46,340 --> 00:44:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] Gle, mi smo...

1142
00:44:48,019 --> 00:44:48,800
[SPEAKER_02] Boji se malo i tako.

1143
00:44:48,800 --> 00:44:52,639
[SPEAKER_01] Boji se, čovjek recimo želi na neku nepravdu upozoriti,

1144
00:44:52,639 --> 00:44:54,599
[SPEAKER_01] otvori taj neki profil,

1145
00:44:54,599 --> 00:44:56,440
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći, obični radnik je negdje

1146
00:44:56,440 --> 00:44:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] ili kotačić u nekom sustavu

1147
00:44:58,320 --> 00:44:58,940
[SPEAKER_01] i to ga smeta.

1148
00:44:58,940 --> 00:45:01,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ili neki moćnik je pored njega susjed,

1149
00:45:01,480 --> 00:45:02,219
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda ga to smeta.

1150
00:45:02,219 --> 00:45:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedna razina

1151
00:45:03,460 --> 00:45:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] i ta razina, to nije nikakav problem.

1152
00:45:05,699 --> 00:45:07,719
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji ova druga, perfidnija razina.

1153
00:45:07,719 --> 00:45:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] A to su ljudi,

1154
00:45:10,159 --> 00:45:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] a to su, ne samo Botov,

1155
00:45:11,300 --> 00:45:12,639
[SPEAKER_01] nego to su ljudi koji su

1156
00:45:12,639 --> 00:45:14,219
[SPEAKER_01] u sustavu,

1157
00:45:14,219 --> 00:45:15,780
[SPEAKER_01] koji su upućeni u sustavu,

1158
00:45:15,780 --> 00:45:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] koji su čak možda na nekim visokim pozicijama

1159
00:45:18,019 --> 00:45:20,320
[SPEAKER_01] nekih stranaka lista, sve jedno.

1160
00:45:20,320 --> 00:45:22,780
[SPEAKER_01] I koji, to se vidi po njihovim komentarima,

1161
00:45:22,780 --> 00:45:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] kad oni govori o nekim ljudima u nadimcima,

1162
00:45:25,079 --> 00:45:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] kad znaju njihove neke,

1163
00:45:26,019 --> 00:45:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] možda i internestovari.

1164
00:45:27,500 --> 00:45:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1165
00:45:27,639 --> 00:45:28,860
[SPEAKER_01] Vidi se da su upućeni.

1166
00:45:29,619 --> 00:45:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] E, i ti ljudi su po meni

1167
00:45:31,079 --> 00:45:32,780
[SPEAKER_01] najveće kukavice,

1168
00:45:32,780 --> 00:45:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno one dosta veliki problem rade,

1169
00:45:34,880 --> 00:45:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] zato što

1170
00:45:36,239 --> 00:45:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] čega se bojiš?

1171
00:45:37,320 --> 00:45:39,480
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto ti imenom i prezemenom

1172
00:45:39,480 --> 00:45:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] ne izađeš van

1173
00:45:40,880 --> 00:45:41,780
[SPEAKER_01] i ne raješ?

1174
00:45:41,780 --> 00:45:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

1175
00:45:43,559 --> 00:45:44,980
[SPEAKER_02] bravo, jer hvala ti na podršci,

1176
00:45:44,980 --> 00:45:46,460
[SPEAKER_02] ali gledaj, ako ja budem na vlasti,

1177
00:45:46,460 --> 00:45:48,119
[SPEAKER_02] ti ćeš opet imat svoj neki nickname.

1178
00:45:48,119 --> 00:45:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, kužim, kužim.

1179
00:45:49,940 --> 00:45:50,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

1180
00:45:50,340 --> 00:45:50,420
[SPEAKER_01] To je to.

1181
00:45:50,420 --> 00:45:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja, koliko god to,

1182
00:45:52,519 --> 00:45:55,280
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, i bilo neugodno nekima,

1183
00:45:55,280 --> 00:45:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] meni je očekivano,

1184
00:45:56,739 --> 00:45:59,599
[SPEAKER_01] jedino mi je nekako i potvrda,

1185
00:45:59,599 --> 00:46:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] da radim, ono,

1186
00:46:01,119 --> 00:46:02,079
[SPEAKER_01] da to radim dobro

1187
00:46:02,079 --> 00:46:04,420
[SPEAKER_01] i da sam nekog ukrao

1188
00:46:04,420 --> 00:46:06,400
[SPEAKER_01] i to, bilo bi to tako povijestino.

1189
00:46:06,400 --> 00:46:08,360
[SPEAKER_02] Eto, postaneš gradonačan i kada očekat ćete

1190
00:46:08,360 --> 00:46:09,619
[SPEAKER_02] sve jednu situaciju od zvijezdi,

1191
00:46:09,619 --> 00:46:10,820
[SPEAKER_02] situacija sa vodom.

1192
00:46:10,820 --> 00:46:11,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ok.

1193
00:46:11,260 --> 00:46:13,320
[SPEAKER_02] Šta bi, kak bi?

1194
00:46:13,320 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako, moram tu naglasiti jednu bitnu stvar,

1195
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:18,860
[SPEAKER_01] a vezano je za ovaj kontekst.

1196
00:46:18,860 --> 00:46:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] Malo sam gledao i ovo što je Mandić pričao,

1197
00:46:22,059 --> 00:46:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] mada vidim i na gradskom vijeću

1198
00:46:23,559 --> 00:46:25,519
[SPEAKER_01] i kako on pokušava nejako sensibilizirati

1199
00:46:25,519 --> 00:46:26,840
[SPEAKER_01] građane oko sebe.

1200
00:46:26,840 --> 00:46:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ti da, kad slušaš njega,

1201
00:46:28,880 --> 00:46:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] kad zažmiriš,

1202
00:46:30,400 --> 00:46:32,239
[SPEAKER_01] ti bi imao dojam da se radi

1203
00:46:32,239 --> 00:46:33,840
[SPEAKER_01] ili osobi koja ima, ne znam,

1204
00:46:33,840 --> 00:46:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] ono, 20-25 godina,

1205
00:46:35,860 --> 00:46:37,860
[SPEAKER_01] ili osobi koja je prvi put u mandatu,

1206
00:46:37,860 --> 00:46:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, on kaže,

1207
00:46:39,260 --> 00:46:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] ono, tko radi taj griješi,

1208
00:46:42,739 --> 00:46:45,360
[SPEAKER_01] ja razumijem građane,

1209
00:46:45,360 --> 00:46:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja se tako sjećam,

1210
00:46:46,380 --> 00:46:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] da, čovječe,

1211
00:46:47,420 --> 00:46:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] ali ti si ovdje već drugi mandat

1212
00:46:49,199 --> 00:46:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] i pucaš na treći mandat.

1213
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:53,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si prije toga bio predsjednik gradskog vijeća,

1214
00:46:53,219 --> 00:46:54,500
[SPEAKER_01] prije toga si bio gradski vijećnik

1215
00:46:54,500 --> 00:46:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] u glavnoj stranci koja vlada grad na 30 godina.

1216
00:46:56,900 --> 00:46:58,860
[SPEAKER_01] Tebi je stranka sve dala da bude študija,

1217
00:46:58,860 --> 00:47:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] jesi bio si uključen u sve moguće odluke te stranke.

1218
00:47:01,820 --> 00:47:04,139
[SPEAKER_01] Sad od jednom u trećem mandatu ti razumiješ građane,

1219
00:47:04,139 --> 00:47:05,320
[SPEAKER_01] ti si jedan od njih,

1220
00:47:05,320 --> 00:47:07,139
[SPEAKER_01] ti si jedan od nas od građana

1221
00:47:07,139 --> 00:47:09,320
[SPEAKER_01] i dajte mi, molim, vas,

1222
00:47:09,320 --> 00:47:11,420
[SPEAKER_01] oprosite jer ja radim pa ja valjda griješim.

1223
00:47:11,500 --> 00:47:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ne. Poanta je da tvoj rad u cijelini,

1224
00:47:13,659 --> 00:47:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] koliko god da ima nekih dobrih stvari

1225
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] kojima sam ja i govorio,

1226
00:47:16,480 --> 00:47:18,659
[SPEAKER_01] je nedovoljan.

1227
00:47:18,659 --> 00:47:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, on je u cijelini za ocjenu 1.

1228
00:47:20,380 --> 00:47:21,320
[SPEAKER_01] I to je to.

1229
00:47:21,320 --> 00:47:24,719
[SPEAKER_01] To što se tiče tokom teksta zvijezde i vode, opću.

1230
00:47:24,719 --> 00:47:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] Što se tiče konkretnih stvari u zvijezdi i vodi,

1231
00:47:26,980 --> 00:47:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] ko nije bio često u gradskoj četvrti,

1232
00:47:31,360 --> 00:47:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] ne zvijezda, nego tamo si izlazil u van,

1233
00:47:32,920 --> 00:47:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] prolazio si iz ekonomske prema Radićevoj,

1234
00:47:35,179 --> 00:47:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] i kroz Radićevoj, prema Korzu.

1235
00:47:37,159 --> 00:47:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] I to je jedan izuzetan problem,

1236
00:47:42,460 --> 00:47:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] jer je to stara jezra.

1237
00:47:43,960 --> 00:47:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] Tu ima svega.

1238
00:47:46,039 --> 00:47:48,219
[SPEAKER_01] Trebalo se naprijed znati kakvi su temelji.

1239
00:47:48,219 --> 00:47:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo situaciju da ljudi koji se bave zvijezdno,

1240
00:47:51,380 --> 00:47:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] kroz povijest,

1241
00:47:52,139 --> 00:47:55,519
[SPEAKER_01] to su ljudi koji u bitnoj mjeri nisu uključeni u,

1242
00:47:55,519 --> 00:47:57,760
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, nisu bili uključeni u tolike pripreme

1243
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] za radove u zvijezdi.

1244
00:47:59,119 --> 00:48:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo do toga da su planovi, projekcije,

1245
00:48:03,460 --> 00:48:05,860
[SPEAKER_01] izgradnje zvijezde ne čuvaju se kod nas u arhivu,

1246
00:48:05,860 --> 00:48:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] nego se čuvaju tamo o Krigs arhivu u Austriji,

1247
00:48:08,139 --> 00:48:09,139
[SPEAKER_01] u Budimpešti.

1248
00:48:09,139 --> 00:48:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto se te kopijeli?

1249
00:48:11,639 --> 00:48:13,280
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto se ni urigiralo preko države,

1250
00:48:13,280 --> 00:48:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] pa preko ambasade, da se to dostavi ovdje?

1251
00:48:15,800 --> 00:48:17,219
[SPEAKER_01] Jel'i smo mi na jako polu kolonija,

1252
00:48:17,219 --> 00:48:18,880
[SPEAKER_01] da ti ne smiješ dobiti ono te papire?

1253
00:48:18,880 --> 00:48:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, puno se prije mogla napraviti priprema,

1254
00:48:21,380 --> 00:48:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] da se točno vidi što, gdje, kako i kada,

1255
00:48:23,800 --> 00:48:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] da ne bude tih problema.

1256
00:48:25,079 --> 00:48:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] To je prva pripremna stvar.

1257
00:48:26,260 --> 00:48:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] Druga stvar je odnos i komunikacija prema ljudima.

1258
00:48:29,420 --> 00:48:31,860
[SPEAKER_01] Dok se ljudi sami nisu počeli jako buniti,

1259
00:48:31,860 --> 00:48:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] dok nije došla voda do grla,

1260
00:48:33,699 --> 00:48:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] žbuka dolje na pod, počela padati,

1261
00:48:36,099 --> 00:48:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] do tad se ništa nije poduzimalo.

1262
00:48:39,199 --> 00:48:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si od početka trebao biti spreman

1263
00:48:41,659 --> 00:48:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] da će to mu datrati 10-15 godina,

1264
00:48:43,380 --> 00:48:44,440
[SPEAKER_01] a ne pokušavati,

1265
00:48:44,440 --> 00:48:47,559
[SPEAKER_01] ako vidiš ranije njegove izjev od Mandića,

1266
00:48:47,559 --> 00:48:48,280
[SPEAKER_01] on je to planirao,

1267
00:48:48,280 --> 00:48:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] najveći dio riješi do izbora.

1268
00:48:49,920 --> 00:48:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, kada je nastala ona panika,

1269
00:48:51,599 --> 00:48:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] onda je dio ljudi počeo odlaziti iz cijelog tog posla.

1270
00:48:54,780 --> 00:48:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] To je druga stvar.

1271
00:48:55,980 --> 00:49:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] Treća stvar je što pitanje vode.

1272
00:49:00,880 --> 00:49:04,360
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je pitanje povjerenja prema gradskoj tvrci vodovod.

1273
00:49:04,360 --> 00:49:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] Mi vidimo, znam, razgovaram s ljudima i na terenu,

1274
00:49:08,420 --> 00:49:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] jako puno inženjera je otišla zadnjih godina iz vodovoda.

1275
00:49:12,920 --> 00:49:16,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi imaju osjećaj da ih se dovoljno ne cijeni,

1276
00:49:16,400 --> 00:49:18,940
[SPEAKER_01] imaju osjećaj da moraju trpiti za tuđu,

1277
00:49:18,940 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] preozimati tuđu odgovornost.

1278
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:23,500
[SPEAKER_01] Najviše radnika u tim gradskim tvrtkama,

1279
00:49:23,500 --> 00:49:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] ključući vodovod,

1280
00:49:24,880 --> 00:49:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] osim inženjera, naravno,

1281
00:49:26,400 --> 00:49:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] nedostaje na terenu, dakle u bazi.

1282
00:49:28,139 --> 00:49:28,719
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

1283
00:49:28,719 --> 00:49:33,199
[SPEAKER_01] A ti zapošljavaš nejakav srednji činovnički sloj.

1284
00:49:33,199 --> 00:49:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, idemo povećati materijalna prava,

1285
00:49:35,519 --> 00:49:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] idemo zaposjetiti dojatnih ljudi dođe.

1286
00:49:37,460 --> 00:49:39,880
[SPEAKER_02] Privatni sektor je konačno otišao, baš ono.

1287
00:49:39,880 --> 00:49:43,199
[SPEAKER_02] Mada znaju reći da se javnom sektoru povećale plaće,

1288
00:49:43,199 --> 00:49:47,400
[SPEAKER_02] ali dobar dio javnog sektora ima malo izdat minimalca.

1289
00:49:47,400 --> 00:49:48,940
[SPEAKER_02] Malo izdat, ali problem je što...

1290
00:49:48,940 --> 00:49:51,300
[SPEAKER_02] To znaš i ti sam, tako da, ali ovo je.

1291
00:49:51,300 --> 00:49:52,980
[SPEAKER_02] Ti ako hoćeš imati dobar inženjera,

1292
00:49:52,980 --> 00:49:55,579
[SPEAKER_02] bila to gradska firma držana, moraš ga platiti.

1293
00:49:55,579 --> 00:49:57,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali još imaš to radnje koji su...

1294
00:49:57,579 --> 00:49:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, inženjer, on je na terenu,

1295
00:49:59,179 --> 00:50:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] zbog uvida, on je uredom.

1296
00:50:00,360 --> 00:50:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, imaš ljude koji rade,

1297
00:50:02,679 --> 00:50:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] znači koji fizički rade te stvari.

1298
00:50:04,539 --> 00:50:06,059
[SPEAKER_01] I ti kada zgovaraš i kada vidiš,

1299
00:50:06,059 --> 00:50:07,659
[SPEAKER_01] naravno da je njima muka od svega,

1300
00:50:07,659 --> 00:50:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] kada su svjedoci da se preko veze,

1301
